1. Variable = acts like a storage or div container
name = "John" => name is the Variable

2. Data Types
a. String => Plain text, enclosed in quotation marks
name = "John"

b. Integer => Counting or Whole number, No quotation marks
age = 15

c. floats => number that has decimals
grade = 3.2

d. Boolean => return whether true or false. variable name normally starts with "is"
is_male = true

e. nil => gives no value for the moment
flaws = nil

